<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Interactive Learning Studio: Python OOP Mastery</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-dark: #0f172a;
            --card-dark: #1e293b;
            --accent-primary: #38bdf8;
            --accent-success: #4ade80;
            --accent-error: #f87171;
            --text-main: #f8fafc;
            --text-muted: #94a3b8;
            --border-color: #334155;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-dark);
            color: var(--text-main);
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding-bottom: 60px;
        }

        header {
            background-color: var(--card-dark);
            padding: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo-area h1 {
            color: var(--accent-primary);
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .progress-container {
            width: 200px;
            background-color: var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 10px;
            position: relative;
            height: 20px;
        }

        .progress-bar {
            width: 0%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: var(--accent-success);
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: width 0.4s ease;
        }

        .progress-text {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            top: 0;
            color: white;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .intro-card, .module-card, .conclusion-card {
            background-color: var(--card-dark);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            color: var(--accent-primary);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-color);
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        h3 {
            color: var(--accent-success);
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .grid-2 {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }

        .info-box {
            background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-primary);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .analogy-box {
            background: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.1);
            border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-success);
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        code, pre {
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            background-color: #0f172a;
            padding: 2px 6px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #e2e8f0;
        }

        pre {
            display: block;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            overflow-x: auto;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .diagram-container {
            background: #0f172a;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: var(--accent-primary);
            color: #0f172a;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            opacity: 0.9;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-success { background-color: var(--accent-success); }
        .btn-disabled { background-color: var(--text-muted); cursor: not-allowed; opacity: 0.5; }

        .quiz-section {
            background: #1e293b;
            border: 1px solid var(--accent-primary);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        .quiz-option {
            background: #0f172a;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            padding: 12px;
            margin: 8px 0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        .quiz-option:hover {
            background: #334155;
        }

        .quiz-option.correct { border-color: var(--accent-success); background: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.2); }
        .quiz-option.wrong { border-color: var(--accent-error); background: rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.2); }

        .feedback { font-weight: bold; margin-top: 10px; display: none; }
        .feedback.correct { color: var(--accent-success); }
        .feedback.wrong { color: var(--accent-error); }

        .locked { opacity: 0.4; pointer-events: none; position: relative; }
        .lock-overlay {
            position: absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%;
            background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7); display: flex; justify-content: center;
            align-items: center; font-size: 24px; color: white; font-weight: bold; z-index: 10;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .printable-btn {
            background: none; border: 1px solid var(--accent-primary); color: var(--accent-primary);
            padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; float: right; margin-top: -40px;
        }

        @media print {
            body { background: white; color: black; }
            .no-print, header, .quiz-section, .btn { display: none !important; }
            .locked { opacity: 1 !important; pointer-events: auto !important; }
            .lock-overlay { display: none !important; }
            .module-card { page-break-after: always; border: none; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="logo-area">
            <h1>Python OOP Mastery</h1>
            <p style="font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted)">Interactive Learning Studio</p>
        </div>
        <div class="no-print" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px;">
            <span>Studio Progress:</span>
            <div class="progress-container">
                <div class="progress-bar" id="master-progress"></div>
                <div class="progress-text" id="progress-text">0%</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        
        <!-- INTRO CARD -->
        <section class="intro-card">
            <h2>Welcome to Python OOP Studio</h2>
            <p>Welcome! This self-contained interactive app will teach you Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) in Python from foundational basics to expert mastery.</p>
            <div class="grid-2">
                <div class="info-box">
                    <strong>⏱️ Est. Time:</strong> 60 Mins<br>
                    <strong>🛠️ Prerequisites:</strong> Basic Python variables & loops.<br>
                    <strong>🎯 Outcome:</strong> Design production-ready Python architectures.
                </div>
                <div class="analogy-box">
                    <strong>🏆 Gamification Reward System:</strong><br>
                    Complete the 4 core modules and pass quizzes to unlock your <strong>Mastery Certificate</strong>.
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="btn" onclick="startLearning()">Get Started</button>
        </section>

        <!-- MODULE 1 -->
        <section class="module-card" id="mod1">
            <button class="printable-btn" onclick="window.print()">🖨️ Print Notes</button>
            <h2>Module 1: Classes and Objects (The Blueprints)</h2>
            <p>A <strong>Class</strong> is a blueprint or template for creating objects. An <strong>Object</strong> is a real-world instance of that blueprint.</p>
            
            <div class="analogy-box">
                <strong>Analogy:</strong> A class is like an architectural blueprint for a house. The house itself built from that blueprint is the Object.
            </div>

            <div class="diagram-container">
                <svg width="400" height="120" viewBox="0 0 400 120">
                    <rect x="10" y="30" width="120" height="60" rx="5" fill="#334155" stroke="#38bdf8" stroke-width="2"/>
                    <text x="70" y="65" fill="white" font-family="sans-serif" text-anchor="middle">Class (Blueprint)</text>
                    <path d="M 140 60 L 240 60" stroke="#4ade80" stroke-width="3" marker-end="url(#arrow)"/>
                    <rect x="260" y="30" width="120" height="60" rx="5" fill="#1e293b" stroke="#4ade80" stroke-width="2"/>
                    <text x="320" y="65" fill="white" font-family="sans-serif" text-anchor="middle">Object (Instance)</text>
                    <defs>
                        <marker id="arrow" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="5" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse">
                          <path d="M 0 0 L 10 5 L 0 10 z" fill="#4ade80"/>
                        </marker>
                    </defs>
                </svg>
